<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Game Changer Team Invitation</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <center>
      <img 
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dnfgu6ltf/image/upload/v1748246990/oetc4chny2o8lxkcocfg.png" 
        width="100px" 
        alt="Game Changer Logo"
      />
      <p style="font-size:20px;"><b>Game Changer Team Invitation!</b></p>
    </center>
    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>You have been invited to join the <strong><%= team %></strong> team on the Game Changer app.</p>

      <p>To accept the invitation and get started:</p>
      <ol>
        <!-- <li>Download the <strong>Game Changer</strong> app from the App Store or Google Play.</li> -->
        <li>Start managing your schedule and team updates with <%= team %> and Jersey No: <strong><%= jersey_no %></strong>.</li>
        <li>Create an account using this email: <strong><%= email %></strong></li>
        <li>Use this temporary password to log in: <strong><%= password %></strong></li>
      </ol>

      <p>Game Changer makes it easy to stay connected, informed, and organized with your team!</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        Best regards,<br />
        The Game Changer Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
